  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.36,
    "endTime": 38.278999999999996,
    "text": "Uh-oh, this isn't looking too good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.36,
    "endTime": 45.86,
    "text": "And by adding your pennies to this jar, we can feed the homeless, help abused animals find good homes, or adopt a child from a third world country."
  },
  {
