    "text": "Something's going on and I don't like this one bit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.339,
    "endTime": 69.019,
    "text": "And the worst thing is, we won't get to save the world anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.68,
    "endTime": 72.98,
    "text": "Oh, why don't you shut up, cry babies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.059,
    "endTime": 75.099,
